content: After extensive testing of both the ipad and android app version of "Talking Garfield" I love the product. That bering said, there are some nuances and inconsistencies that could be synced up. The ipad app crashes whenever I take a photo with the selfie camera. The android version doesn't even have the option to use the selfie camera. I also cannot seem to make Garfield repeat my words on either platform though. I find this viscerally dissatisfying. I would still buy this app another two times times again if I could----BUT this is not an offically licensed Paws.
